# .secret-scan-ignore
#
# List file patterns (one per line) to exclude from secret scanning.
# These are passed as --exclude arguments to grep.
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.

# Example config file contains placeholder values, not real secrets
chef-pkg.toml.example

# Test fixtures may contain fake credentials
*_test.go

# Spec and docs may reference example values
.claude/specification.md
